# This is an LZA-only Landing Zone example (AWS Control Tower + Landing Zone
# Accelerator YAML). It ships no Terraform/OpenTofu/CDK, so this ignore list
# focuses on secrets and local/editor noise rather than IaC state.

# Secrets / real values — never commit. Replace PLACEHOLDER_ tokens with real
# account IDs / ARNs in your own private fork, not here. See PLACEHOLDERS.md.
*.env
.env
secrets.*
*.local.yaml
*.local.yml

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
